parameterDefinitions.description: Update center url used for the test
parameterDefinitions.name: updateCenterUrl

parameterDefinitions.description:
groupId/artifactId for the parent pom which will be used.
Note : If you let this field empty, every, a test on every already tested core versions (in report XML file) will be made.
parameterDefinitions.name: parentCoordinates

parameterDefinitions.description:
You can fix a version in there, if you don't want to rely on "the latest core version retrieved in update center"
If you selected the blank parentCoordinates, let this field empty please.
parameterDefinitions.name: parentVersion

parameterDefinitions.description:
Comma separated plugin names you want to test.
Note : If you let this field empty, every plugins residing in update center will be tested
parameterDefinitions.name: includePlugins

parameterDefinitions.description:
Comma separated plugin names you DON'T want to test.
Note : If you let this field empty, the includePlugins policy defined below will be applied "as is"
List of default excluded plugins (and reason why excluded) :
  • ci-game : Seems like on old hudsons, it doesn't work
parameterDefinitions.name: excludePlugins

parameterDefinitions.description: Allow to skip plugin-compat-tester unit tests
parameterDefinitions.name: maven.test.skip

parameterDefinitions.description: Allows to skip test cache. For example when you want to force testing of some plugins
parameterDefinitions.name: skipTestCache

parameterDefinitions.description:
Allows to define a minimal cache threshold for test status.
That is to say, every results lower than this threshold won't be considered as part of the cache.
Selecting INTERNAL_ERROR here is the same as checking the skipTestCache checkbox.
parameterDefinitions.name: cacheThresholdStatus

parameterDefinitions.description:
Test cache timeout allows to not perform compatibility test over some plugins if compatibility test was performed recently.
Cache timeout is given in milliseconds.
parameterDefinitions.name: testCacheTimeout
